{"tid":1006273,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[有片] 拒交陀地費遭圍毆　菜館東主：江湖事　江湖了","createTime":"2019-02-02T23:48:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-03T11:25:30.000Z","uid":224066,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"113f7d6db274d462d1be6fcc3b9606af9d467a09","tid":1006273,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T23:48:43.000Z","msg":"繼周日長沙灣東京街一間潮州菜館遭惡漢掃場刑毀後，深水埗元州街一間潮州菜館的東主，昨凌晨遭多名戴口罩男子持木棍闖入店內毆打，繼而被拉出店外圍毆，歹徒逞兇後逃去，警員接報趕至拘捕一名懷疑與歹徒同行負責把風的女子。據稱，較早時有自稱黑社會抬年桔上門向東主收陀地費，東主斷言拒絕，懷疑有人因此報復。東主頭部受傷但拒絕送院，事後脫去染血上衣露出紋身，揚言「江湖事，江湖了」，案件交由深水埗警區反黑組調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=M_axeTZNVX4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DM_axeTZNVX4&d=6VpbUQS5Cy4QwgKrD6%2Fp7pggdM0W6%2BkgeusliPwa7Y4%3D&h=1963ccf8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=M_axeTZNVX4</a>"},{"pid":"36e9f829cd68ce5edefa5c07b7bf789885ca9d43","tid":1006273,"uid":90820,"like":3,"dislike":25,"score":-22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T00:35:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>東主頭部受傷但拒絕送院，事後脫去染血上衣露出紋身，揚言「江湖事，江湖了」，案件交由深水埗警區反黑組調查。<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n畀人打到頭破血流<br />\n人哋走晒先除衫話要江湖事江湖了<br />\n走住嚟屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dff031bc1f4a038a0e88656148659f812aeb7357","tid":1006273,"uid":32723,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T00:49:59.000Z","msg":"D待應,收銀, 大廚洗碗全部炒得啦<br />\n<br />\n咁多人打老闆都唔幫拖<br />\n<br />\n定係老闆平時對伙記都唔好<br />\n<br />\n今次打佢大快人心?"},{"pid":"8623ac71120b0dc0d887cc984a5f6e03ffd14705","tid":1006273,"uid":157510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T00:51:56.000Z","msg":"打完先江湖事江湖了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"531cf9b69a247c820fd97d79abf55dfdfb3bfa17","tid":1006273,"uid":20658,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"re